The '''Commissioner of Trade''' was a position within both the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], although the position was limited, and the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] government. The being who held this title handled matters of trade and ensured that citizens of the New Republic would be able to conduct business safely.

